summary: General fire information for Sand Fire
Evacuations:
Evacuation Advisory has been lifted.  Fire personnel are extinguishing hot spots.
The evacuation center closed on June 10th.
Road Closures: Hwy 16 opened at 12:00 p.m. today.  Please be aware of emergency vehicles in the fire area.
Cooperating Agencies: CAL FIRE, Cal OES, Yolo County Sheriff, CHP, NBIMT and multiple local government  fire agencies.
Conditions: Cooling temps will aid in suppression efforts.  Fire behavior expected to be minimal.
